{"id": "JSON-001", "query": "列出三种编程语言的名称和它们各自最擅长的领域。请用JSON格式回答，格式为: {\"languages\": [{\"name\": \"...\", \"strength\": \"...\"}]}", "response": "{\"languages\": [{\"name\": \"Python\", \"strength\": \"数据科学和AI\"}, {\"name\": \"JavaScript\", \"strength\": \"Web前端开发\"}, {\"name\": \"Go\", \"strength\": \"高并发后端服务\"}]}", "expected_schema": {"type": "object", "required": ["languages"], "properties": {"languages": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["name", "strength"]}}}}, "tier": "smoke"}
{"id": "JSON-002", "query": "JSON 格式输出：一个学生对象，包含姓名、年龄（整数）、成绩（数组，含三科分数）。", "response": "{\"name\": \"张三\", \"age\": 20, \"scores\": [85, 92, 78]}", "expected_schema": {"type": "object", "required": ["name", "age", "scores"], "properties": {"name": {"type": "string"}, "age": {"type": "integer"}, "scores": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "number"}, "minItems": 3, "maxItems": 3}}}, "tier": "full"}
{"id": "JSON-003", "query": "用 JSON 列出两个城市的天气信息，每个城市包含：城市名、温度（数字）、天气描述（字符串）。", "response": "{\"cities\": [{\"name\": \"北京\", \"temperature\": 28, \"weather\": \"晴\"}, {\"name\": \"上海\", \"temperature\": 32, \"weather\": \"多云转阵雨\"}]}", "expected_schema": {"type": "object", "required": ["cities"], "properties": {"cities": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "required": ["name", "temperature", "weather"]}}}}, "tier": "full"}
{"id": "JSON-004", "query": "JSON格式回答：一本图书的信息，包含书名、作者、出版年份（整数）、价格（数字）、是否有库存（布尔值）。", "response": "{\"title\": \"三体\", \"author\": \"刘慈欣\", \"year\": 2008, \"price\": 39.9, \"in_stock\": true}", "expected_schema": {"type": "object", "required": ["title", "author", "year", "price", "in_stock"], "properties": {"title": {"type": "string"}, "author": {"type": "string"}, "year": {"type": "integer"}, "price": {"type": "number"}, "in_stock": {"type": "boolean"}}}, "tier": "full"}
{"id": "JSON-005", "query": "用 JSON 格式返回一个 REST API 的响应结构示例，包含 status（整数）、message（字符串）、data（对象，包含 id 和 name）。", "response": "{\"status\": 200, \"message\": \"success\", \"data\": {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"示例数据\"}}", "expected_schema": {"type": "object", "required": ["status", "message", "data"], "properties": {"status": {"type": "integer"}, "message": {"type": "string"}, "data": {"type": "object", "required": ["id", "name"]}}}, "tier": "full"}
